casebody.data:
Michelle Stopyra YANEY, Petitioner,
v.
SUPERIOR COURT OF CALIFORNIA, San Bernardino County. No. 19-5165 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of California dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
